{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I've spent the last decade"},{"time":2000,"text":"subjecting myself to pain and humiliation,"},{"time":5000,"text":"hopefully for a good cause,"},{"time":7000,"text":"which is self-improvement."},{"time":10000,"text":"And I've done this in three parts."},{"time":12000,"text":"So first I started with the mind."},{"time":15000,"text":"And I decided to try to get smarter"},{"time":19000,"text":"by reading the entire Encyclopedia Britannica"},{"time":21000,"text":"from A to Z --"},{"time":23000,"text":"or, more precisely, from \"a-ak\" to \"Zywiec.\""},{"time":26000,"text":"And here's a little image of that."},{"time":28000,"text":"And this was an amazing year."},{"time":30000,"text":"It was really a fascinating journey."},{"time":32000,"text":"It was painful at times,"},{"time":35000,"text":"especially for those around me."},{"time":37000,"text":"My wife started to fine me one dollar"},{"time":40000,"text":"for every irrelevant fact I inserted into conversation."},{"time":43000,"text":"So it had its downsides."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47000,"text":"But after that,"},{"time":49000,"text":"I decided to work on the spirit."},{"time":51000,"text":"As I mentioned last year,"},{"time":53000,"text":"I grew up with no religion at all."},{"time":55000,"text":"I'm Jewish,"},{"time":57000,"text":"but I'm Jewish in the same way the Olive Garden is Italian."},{"time":60000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":62000,"text":"Not really."},{"time":64000,"text":"But I decided to learn about the Bible and my heritage"},{"time":67000,"text":"by actually diving in"},{"time":69000,"text":"and trying to live it and immerse myself in it."},{"time":71000,"text":"So I decided to follow all the rules of the Bible."},{"time":74000,"text":"And from the Ten Commandments"},{"time":76000,"text":"to growing my beard --"},{"time":78000,"text":"because Leviticus says you cannot shave."},{"time":80000,"text":"So this is what I looked like by the end."},{"time":83000,"text":"Thank you for that reaction."},{"time":85000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":88000,"text":"I look a little like Moses, or Ted Kaczynski."},{"time":91000,"text":"I got both of them."},{"time":93000,"text":"So there was the topiary there."},{"time":96000,"text":"And there's the sheep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99000,"text":"Now the final part of the trilogy"},{"time":101000,"text":"was I wanted to focus on the body"},{"time":104000,"text":"and try to be the healthiest person I could be,"},{"time":106000,"text":"the healthiest person alive."},{"time":108000,"text":"So that's what I've been doing the last couple of years."},{"time":111000,"text":"And I just finished a couple of months ago."},{"time":113000,"text":"And I have to say, thank God."},{"time":115000,"text":"Because living so healthily was killing me."},{"time":118000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":120000,"text":"It was so overwhelming,"},{"time":123000,"text":"because the amount of things you have to do,"},{"time":125000,"text":"it's just mind-boggling."},{"time":127000,"text":"I was listening to all the experts"},{"time":129000,"text":"and talking to sort of a board of medical advisers."},{"time":131000,"text":"And they were telling me"},{"time":133000,"text":"all the things I had to do."},{"time":135000,"text":"I had to eat right,"},{"time":137000,"text":"exercise, meditate, pet dogs,"},{"time":140000,"text":"because that lowers the blood pressure."},{"time":142000,"text":"I wrote the book on a treadmill,"},{"time":144000,"text":"and it took me about a thousand miles"},{"time":146000,"text":"to write the book."},{"time":148000,"text":"I had to put on sunscreen."},{"time":150000,"text":"This was no small feat,"},{"time":152000,"text":"because if you listen to dermatologists,"},{"time":154000,"text":"they say that you should have a shot glass full of sunscreen."},{"time":157000,"text":"And you have to reapply it every two to four hours."},{"time":159000,"text":"So I think half of my book advance"},{"time":161000,"text":"went into sunscreen."},{"time":163000,"text":"I was like a glazed doughnut"},{"time":165000,"text":"for most of the year."},{"time":167000,"text":"There was the washing of hands."},{"time":169000,"text":"I had to do that properly."},{"time":171000,"text":"And my immunologist told me"},{"time":173000,"text":"that I should also wipe down"},{"time":176000,"text":"all of the remote controls and iPhones in my house,"},{"time":179000,"text":"because those are just orgies of germs."},{"time":182000,"text":"So that took a lot of time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184000,"text":"I also tried to be the safest person I could be,"},{"time":187000,"text":"because that's a part of health."},{"time":189000,"text":"I was inspired"},{"time":191000,"text":"by the Danish Safety Council."},{"time":193000,"text":"They started a public campaign"},{"time":195000,"text":"that says, \"A walking helmet is a good helmet.\""},{"time":198000,"text":"So they believe you should not just wear helmets for biking,"},{"time":202000,"text":"but also for walking around."},{"time":205000,"text":"And you can see there"},{"time":208000,"text":"they're shopping with their helmets."},{"time":210000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":212000,"text":"Well yeah, I tried that."},{"time":216000,"text":"Now it's a little extreme, I admit."},{"time":218000,"text":"But if you think about this,"},{"time":220000,"text":"this is actually -- the \"Freakonomics\" authors wrote about this --"},{"time":223000,"text":"that more people die on a per mile basis"},{"time":226000,"text":"from drunk walking"},{"time":228000,"text":"than from drunk driving."},{"time":230000,"text":"So something to think about tonight"},{"time":232000,"text":"if you've had a couple."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235000,"text":"So I finished,"},{"time":237000,"text":"and it was a success in a sense."},{"time":239000,"text":"All of the markers went in the right direction."},{"time":242000,"text":"My cholesterol went down, I lost weight,"},{"time":245000,"text":"my wife stopped telling me that I looked pregnant."},{"time":249000,"text":"So that was nice."},{"time":252000,"text":"And it was successful overall."},{"time":255000,"text":"But I also learned that I was too healthy,"},{"time":257000,"text":"and that was unhealthy."},{"time":259000,"text":"I was so focused on doing all these things"},{"time":262000,"text":"that I was neglecting my friends and family."},{"time":265000,"text":"And as Dan Buettner can tell you,"},{"time":267000,"text":"having a strong social network"},{"time":269000,"text":"is so crucial to our health."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271000,"text":"So I finished."},{"time":273000,"text":"And I kind of went overboard"},{"time":276000,"text":"on the week after the project was over."},{"time":279000,"text":"I went to the dark side,"},{"time":281000,"text":"and I just indulged myself."},{"time":283000,"text":"It was like something out of Caligula."},{"time":285000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":287000,"text":"Without the sex part."},{"time":289000,"text":"Because I have three young kids,"},{"time":291000,"text":"so that wasn't happening."},{"time":294000,"text":"But the over-eating and over-drinking, definitely."},{"time":297000,"text":"And I finally have stabilized."},{"time":302000,"text":"So now I'm back"},{"time":304000,"text":"to adopting many -- not all; I don't wear a helmet anymore --"},{"time":307000,"text":"but dozens of healthy behaviors"},{"time":310000,"text":"that I adopted during my year."},{"time":313000,"text":"It was really a life-changing project."},{"time":316000,"text":"And I, of course, don't have time to go into all of them."},{"time":319000,"text":"Let me just tell you two really quickly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322000,"text":"The first is -- and this was surprising to me;"},{"time":324000,"text":"I didn't expect this to come out --"},{"time":326000,"text":"but I live a much quieter life now."},{"time":329000,"text":"Because we live in such a noisy world."},{"time":332000,"text":"There's trains and planes and cars"},{"time":336000,"text":"and Bill O'Reilly, he's very noisy."},{"time":339000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":342000,"text":"And this is a real underestimated, under-appreciated health hazard --"},{"time":347000,"text":"not just because it harms our hearing, which it obviously does,"},{"time":350000,"text":"but it actually initiates"},{"time":353000,"text":"the fight-or-flight response."},{"time":355000,"text":"A loud noise will get your fight-or-flight response going."},{"time":358000,"text":"And this, over the years,"},{"time":361000,"text":"can cause real damage, cardiovascular damage."},{"time":364000,"text":"The World Health Organization just did a big study"},{"time":367000,"text":"that they published this year."},{"time":369000,"text":"And it was done in Europe."},{"time":371000,"text":"And they estimated"},{"time":373000,"text":"that 1.6 million years of healthy living"},{"time":377000,"text":"are lost every year in Europe"},{"time":380000,"text":"because of noise pollution."},{"time":383000,"text":"So they think it's actually very deadly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386000,"text":"And by the way,"},{"time":388000,"text":"it's also terrible for your brain."},{"time":391000,"text":"It really impairs cognition."},{"time":394000,"text":"And our Founding Fathers knew about this."},{"time":396000,"text":"When they wrote the Constitution,"},{"time":398000,"text":"they put dirt all over the cobblestones outside the hall"},{"time":402000,"text":"so that they could concentrate."},{"time":405000,"text":"So without noise reduction technology,"},{"time":408000,"text":"our country would not exist."},{"time":411000,"text":"So as a patriot,"},{"time":413000,"text":"I felt it was important to --"},{"time":415000,"text":"I wear all the earplugs and the earphones,"},{"time":417000,"text":"and it's really improved my life"},{"time":420000,"text":"in a surprising and unexpected way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423000,"text":"And the second point I want to make, the final point,"},{"time":426000,"text":"is that -- and it's actually been a theme of TEDMED --"},{"time":431000,"text":"that joy is so important to your health,"},{"time":435000,"text":"that very few of these behaviors"},{"time":439000,"text":"will stick with me"},{"time":441000,"text":"unless there's some sense of pleasure and joy in them."},{"time":446000,"text":"And just to give you one instance of this:"},{"time":449000,"text":"food."},{"time":451000,"text":"The junk food industry"},{"time":454000,"text":"is really great"},{"time":456000,"text":"at pressing our pleasure buttons"},{"time":458000,"text":"and figuring out what's the most pleasurable."},{"time":461000,"text":"But I think we can use their techniques"},{"time":463000,"text":"and apply them to healthy food."},{"time":465000,"text":"To give just one example,"},{"time":467000,"text":"we love crunchiness, mouthfeel."},{"time":470000,"text":"So I basically have tried to incorporate crunchiness"},{"time":474000,"text":"into a lot of my recipes --"},{"time":476000,"text":"throw in some sunflower seeds."},{"time":478000,"text":"And you can almost trick yourself"},{"time":480000,"text":"into thinking you're eating Doritos."},{"time":482000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":484000,"text":"And it has made me a healthier person."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486000,"text":"So that is it."},{"time":488000,"text":"The book about it comes out in April."},{"time":490000,"text":"It's called \"Drop Dead Healthy.\""},{"time":492000,"text":"And I hope that I don't get sick during the book tour."},{"time":494000,"text":"That's my greatest hope."}]},{"cues":[{"time":496000,"text":"So thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}